人都可以靠自己啊"},{"pid":"cd7ddecda4d0dc0619a88150e86e9b4d5fa39075","tid":1578920,"uid":69334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T11:21:52.000Z","msg":"坐左幾耐？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fbd93cd54038dea143eea6509970f52f643b359","tid":1578920,"uid":34927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cd7ddecda4d0dc0619a88150e86e9b4d5fa39075","tid":1578920,"uid":69334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T11:21:52.000Z","msg":"坐左幾耐？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T11:25:38.000Z","msg":"坐左好耐啊真係 個眾籌之後點？"},{"pid":"d3a7923226320054dac9bde0415d527c1011a3c2","tid":1578920,"uid":278786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T18:17:21.000Z","msg":"如何做到有一百萬人以上，對和理非而言，最重要是不用申請不反對通知書而且有合法途徑。否則乜文宣都無用。<br />\n有條橋，就是抄何妖，佢話921清潔香港不用申請不反對通知書，仲串到撤銷遊行申請。<br />\n咁佢無被人拉無人告，心理上就可以宣傳：我地9.29搞的都是清潔香港行動，沿港島電車路線，人人執拉圾。<br />\n<br />\n人流控制方面：<br />\n可以呼籲港島人在自己區清潔；<br />\n九龍東人在鰂魚涌的香港殯儀館（象徵送中）以東，新界東人在鰂魚涌以西;<br />\n九龍西人在中環遮打花園以西，新界西人在中環以東。<br />\n<br />\n另一個重點，係需要有號召力的人或機構呼籲，大肆宣傳，俾和理非感覺既合法又多人陪，咁就安心參加。<br />\n<br />\n利申：和理非"},{"pid":"d4e09087b400b23b32f6aa4ffc28e0a4f9af6e0e","tid":1578920,"uid":223609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T07:36:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36b055937b53e405ef1580b5f8cfaf794ee27d0c","tid":1578920,"uid":106336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T07:36:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}